    "Specifically, we investigate the impingement of D 0 = 2.2 -2.3 mm water droplets on structured hydrophobic Polydimethylsiloxane (PDMS) and hydrophilic polylactide (PLA) substrates, at velocities ranging from U 0 = 0.43 -0.88 m/s.",
